      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just... it's not just sadness. it's like the world has lost all its color. i look at my stuff, the house, everything we built together, and it just feels like a museum of a life i dont live anymore. staying here just feels like i'm performing a role in a play that ended a long time ago. what's the point of pretending to be a person when the person i actually was is gone too?",
